sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant PublishUI as Dashboard Blogs or Projects UI
    participant ContentAPI as POST or PATCH /api/blogs or /api/projects
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (Prisma)
    participant CampaignAPI as POST /api/subscribers/campaigns
    participant Queue as Job Queue or Batch Worker
    participant MailService as Mail Service (Nodemailer)
    participant GmailSMTP as Gmail SMTP
    participant Subscriber as Subscriber Inbox

    Admin->>PublishUI: Publish article/blog/project
    PublishUI->>ContentAPI: Save content with status=published
    ContentAPI->>DB: Upsert content row and publishedAt
    DB-->>ContentAPI: Persisted content
    ContentAPI->>CampaignAPI: Trigger newsletter campaign

    CampaignAPI->>DB: Read active subscribers
    DB-->>CampaignAPI: Subscriber batch
    CampaignAPI->>Queue: Enqueue send jobs (batched)

    loop For each batch
        Queue->>MailService: Build campaign template with content link
        MailService->>GmailSMTP: sendMail(batch recipients)
        GmailSMTP-->>MailService: Accepted or rejected per recipient
        MailService->>DB: Record delivery status and retries
        DB-->>MailService: Status persisted
    end

    Queue-->>CampaignAPI: Campaign completed summary
    CampaignAPI-->>PublishUI: Delivery metrics (sent, failed, retried)
    PublishUI-->>Admin: Show publish + email campaign result
    GmailSMTP-->>Subscriber: Newsletter arrives with new content link
